          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1604489775167-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> </strong>linguine for 7-9 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the linguine, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
