    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the linguine is cooking, chop the <strong>brie </strong>into small pieces</p><p>Peel the <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Crumble the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
